[tb_start_text mode=1 ]
#Kai
My name is Kai, i'm his Death's Messenger.[p]
The person who delivers his final wish to exchange for his soul: to be able to live again, make use of his talents and wealth in a good way and make you happy.[p]
I, however, couldn't afford to erase his death so i asked him if i could live in his position as dr Quang instead and the old man agreed. So i changed reality according to his wish and met you[p]
[_tb_end_text]

