He might have made mistakes and paid with loneliness for a long time but that doesn't mean he should feel like erasing his life. [p]
If only i managed to be there for him in his final days maybe i could convince him to change his mind. No one deserved to die this lonely[p]
[_tb_end_text]

[tb_start_text mode=1 ]
